  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field__item\" property=\"schema:text\"><p> </p><p><strong>Presented by Liberty Mutual Insurance</strong></p><p><span>On average, 75 percent of commercial insureds may be under-valued.” If property valuation is not calculated regularly, your organization’s property could be improperly insured, meaning that your coverage may be less than sufficient in the case of damage or disaster. Learn more from Liberty Mutual.</span></p><p><a href=\"https://business.libertymutual.com/insights/more-accuracy-less-risk-the-benefits-of-regular-property-valuation/\"><strong>Read more &gt;</strong></a></p></div></body></html>",
